WEBVTT

00:00:04.240 --> 00:00:07.780
ir gedenkt vi azoy ir hot bakumen di falshe papirn in, Berlin?

00:00:07.605 --> 00:00:08.579
yo.

00:00:08.229 --> 00:00:09.692
