00:00:09.444 --> 00:00:14.318
ikh bin geven in a groyse shtub. m'hot arayngeshtupt dort ale

00:00:14.318 --> 00:00:15.615
shikses

00:00:15.671 --> 00:00:17.541
un m'hot oysgeforsht.

00:00:17.541 --> 00:00:21.218
m'hot, tsi di, ver zey zenen, fun vanet zey zenen.

00:00:21.273 --> 00:00:23.580
ikh hob gornisht gehat keyn papirn.

00:00:23.670 --> 00:00:26.314
hob ikh gezogt "ikh bin a, a polke."

00:00:26.741 --> 00:00:27.785
vos hob ikh gekent

00:00:27.785 --> 00:00:31.512
azoy hot mir tsugeshtekt di revolver tsum ponem.

00:00:32.073 --> 00:00:33.435
un m'hot aykh gegleybt?

00:00:33.407 --> 00:00:34.358
nu?

00:00:34.358 --> 00:00:36.220
ikh bin geblibn lebn.

00:00:36.528 --> 00:00:38.784
hobn zey gemuzt gleybn.

00:00:39.617 --> 00:00:43.090
vos makht ir itstert in pensye, un vos tut ir?

00:00:39.667 --> 00:00:40.641
zenen

00:00:42.958 --> 00:00:44.390
in pensye

00:00:43.980 --> 00:00:45.012
yo.

00:00:44.865 --> 00:00:46.600
ikh tu gornisht.

00:00:46.600 --> 00:00:48.218
ikh drey mikh arum.

00:00:49.337 --> 00:00:51.036
ir hot epes familye?

00:00:51.632 --> 00:00:52.454
neyn.

00:00:52.442 --> 00:00:54.350
khuts di kinder mit di tokhter?

00:00:52.492 --> 00:00:57.094
go- akhuts di kinder dos iz mayn gantse mishpokhe.

00:00:56.947 --> 00:00:58.950
un zey kumen aykh zen, ir zent

00:00:58.870 --> 00:01:02.274
nisht azoy fil, ikh farlang nisht fun zey.

00:01:02.415 --> 00:01:05.363
fraytik un shabes kumt men mikh nemen.

00:01:05.452 --> 00:01:09.193
yedn fraytik un shabes? ir shloft bay zey?

00:01:06.482 --> 00:01:08.226
yo, un

00:01:08.226 --> 00:01:11.354
ikh shlof bay zey, un me brengt mikh tsurik.

00:01:11.460 --> 00:01:13.615
ikh hob nisht tsu zey keyn TAANOT.

00:01:13.653 --> 00:01:16.095
vayl zey zenen arbeter mentshn

00:01:16.100 --> 00:01:17.768
un zey hobn kinder.

00:01:17.768 --> 00:01:19.723
zey hobn BAAYOT bay zikh.

00:01:20.133 --> 00:01:22.406
vi azoy filt ir zikh mitn gezunt?

00:01:22.412 --> 00:01:23.808
nisht spetsyel.

00:01:26.968 --> 00:01:28.414
nisht spetsyel.

00:01:28.807 --> 00:01:31.840
vi azoy filt ir UNK tsu DEUTSCHLAND itstert?

00:01:31.811 --> 00:01:33.595
az zey zoln vern farkhapt.

00:01:33.887 --> 00:01:35.571
ikh kuk a film.

00:01:35.571 --> 00:01:37.276
ikh ze a DEUTSCH.

00:01:37.276 --> 00:01:38.961
ikh farmakh glaykh.

00:01:39.422 --> 00:01:40.936
ikh ken nisht gut

00:01:41.413 --> 00:01:42.840
un di poylishn?

00:01:42.712 --> 00:01:46.295
oykh nisht. di polyakn mit di DEUTSCHEN tsuzamen.

00:01:46.295 --> 00:01:47.972
zoln brenen vi ⟨kien⟩.

00:01:48.669 --> 00:01:52.140
vi azoy hot ir oysgekhovet di kinder? ir hot zey dertseylt

00:01:52.162 --> 00:01:56.342
zey veysn. zey hobn gantse bikher.

00:01:55.475 --> 00:01:58.182
ober ven UNK geven kleyn flegt ir zey dertseyln

00:01:58.187 --> 00:02:00.308
vos ir z- vos ir zent durkhgegan?

00:01:58.305 --> 00:01:59.650
vi, vos

00:02:00.380 --> 00:02:03.075
 m- m'hot geflegt tsu redn.

00:02:03.300 --> 00:02:09.709
un vi azoy iz geven mit dem esn? zey, zey hobn gemuzt esn tsi neyn? m'hot gekent iberlozn dos esn?

00:02:09.559 --> 00:02:11.529
ver, di kinder?

00:02:10.260 --> 00:02:11.546
di kinder.

00:02:11.957 --> 00:02:15.850
yo, zey hobn, zey hobn dafke ge- zenen voyl geven.

00:02:17.745 --> 00:02:20.374
v- vi azoy filt ir itster tsum

00:02:20.374 --> 00:02:23.970
tsum frumkeyt? ir zent frum? ir geyt in shul, ir

00:02:23.482 --> 00:02:26.649
neyn, neyn. ikh gey gornisht.

00:02:26.739 --> 00:02:29.518
s'iz mir n- ikh volt shoyn nisht gevolt lebn.

00:02:30.587 --> 00:02:32.067
far vos far UNK

00:02:32.072 --> 00:02:35.459
ikh ze di kinder mutshen zikh lebn mir oykh.

00:02:35.565 --> 00:02:37.028
ikh bin aleyn.

00:02:37.202 --> 00:02:40.606
undz filt mir bay nakht shlekht oder vos

00:02:40.661 --> 00:02:44.250
nishto ver. ikh hob gemakht azan zeyger

00:02:44.458 --> 00:02:46.427
oder ikh bin nokh fort aleyn.

00:02:46.533 --> 00:02:48.469
fir tog bin ikh aleyn.

00:02:48.862 --> 00:02:53.346
oft hob ikh geklungen tsu nokh a UNK ⟨tsi ken⟩ kumen, zi ken nisht kumen.

00:02:55.157 --> 00:02:58.777
ir kholemt fun vos iz geven bay nakht? hot ir khaloymes?

00:02:58.498 --> 00:02:59.398
yo.

00:02:59.200 --> 00:03:00.410
vos kholemt ir?

00:03:00.270 --> 00:03:02.391
ah, ikh kholem

00:03:02.430 --> 00:03:05.834
ah, az a doytsh kumt. er shtikt mikh.

00:03:05.889 --> 00:03:07.768
er vil mikh derhargenen.

00:03:07.768 --> 00:03:08.755
shtendik.

00:03:08.755 --> 00:03:11.371
ven yetst bin ikh dokh aleyn.

00:03:11.514 --> 00:03:13.759
